WEBVTT

00:05:30.626 --> 00:05:33.088
not from crime, not from theft,

00:05:34.149 --> 00:05:37.117
but from the fact
that the building you're in --

00:05:37.141 --> 00:05:38.347
the building you're in --

00:05:38.371 --> 00:05:40.304
might not be structurally sound

00:05:41.268 --> 00:05:43.871
or built from nontoxic components

00:05:43.895 --> 00:05:46.628
or meet local natural disaster standards.

00:05:48.926 --> 00:05:50.823
It's the 21st century.

00:05:51.760 --> 00:05:54.299
And this just isn't good enough.

00:05:57.395 --> 00:05:59.667
What if -- what if --